<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
    <h2 style="color: #333; text-align: center;">Trendupp Verification</h2>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>Your one-time password (OTP) for Trendupp is:</p>
    <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #4A90E2; margin: 30px 0;">
        <%= otp %>
    </div>
    <p>This code will expire in 10 minutes. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888; text-align: center;">&copy; 2026 Trendupp. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>
